OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1773259871
OL,3,CDisgraced politician suspended for
OL,4,Cthird time in six months
OL,6,FDisgraced Jersey politician Deputy
OL,7,FPhilip Ozouf has been suspended from
OL,8,Foffice for the third time in six
OL,9,Fmonths, following his conviction for
OL,10,Fimmigration offences.
OL,12,FThe Privileges and Procedures
OL,13,FCommittee said they considered Ozouf's
OL,14,Factions a breach of the Code of
OL,15,FConduct because his actions had a lack
OL,16,Fof regard for the island's laws and
OL,17,Fjudicial process and had damaged the
OL,18,Fintegrity and reputation of the
OL,19,FAssembly.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
