FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1773259871
OL,3,CDisgraced politician suspended for
OL,4,Cthird time in six months
OL,6,FIt comes after he was sentenced to 120
OL,7,Fhours of community service last month
OL,8,Ffor employing five Rwandan nationals
OL,9,Fin his laundry business without the
OL,10,Fcorrect work permits.
OL,12,FAfter a motion to delay the debate due
OL,13,Fto Ozouf's poor health was refused,
OL,14,Fthe Jersey States Assembly backed a 28-
OL,15,Fday suspension without pay by 34 votes
OL,16,Fto 5, with 6 abstentions.
OL,18,FOzouf was absent and did not defend
OL,19,Fhimself, as he had called in sick.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1773259871
OL,3,CDisgraced politician suspended for
OL,4,Cthird time in six months
OL,6,FThe Committee claim Ozouf breached
OL,7,Frules six and seven of the Code of
OL,8,FConduct.
OL,10,FRule six states that "members must not
OL,11,Fact or behave in a manner in the
OL,12,Fcourse of their public and private
OL,13,Flife" that brings the Assembly or its
OL,14,FMembers "generally into disrepute and
OL,15,Fshould conduct themselves in a manner
OL,16,Fwhich strengthens the public's trust
OL,17,Fand confidence" in Jersey States.
OL,19,FMeanwhile, rule seven explains that
OL,20,Fpoliticians "must uphold the law in
OL,21,Faccordance with their oath of office".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
