PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1773259871
OL,3,CDisgraced politician suspended for
OL,4,Cthird time in six months
OL,6,FA suspended member of the states
OL,7,Fcannot:
OL,9,FOzouf was first suspended from the
OL,10,FStates without pay last September
OL,11,Fafter being convicted of motoring
OL,12,Foffences and failing to attend parish
OL,13,Fhall inquiries.
OL,15,FHe was then suspended for a second
OL,16,Ftime in November - this time with pay
OL,17,F- after pleading guilty to breaking
OL,18,Fimmigration law.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
